 *1. Gemini Text Generation Module* (Idea Generator)

* Uses *Google Gemini Flash / Flash Lite* model
* Generates *5 YouTube video ideas* based on a topic
* Works only with *Google API Key*
* No image generation happens in this module
* Runs fast and light

*Flow:*


User Topic â†’ Gemini Model â†’ 5 YouTube Ideas


---

## *2. SD-Turbo Thumbnail Generation Module* (Image Generator)

* Runs *locally* using diffusers library
* Uses *StabilityAI SD-Turbo model* (very fast)
* Does *NOT require any API key*
* Generates highâ€‘quality thumbnails from idea + description

*Flow:*


Idea + Description â†’ SD-Turbo â†’ YouTube Thumbnail (PNG)


